{
  "id": "adv_card_kor_05_01",
  "title": "fran 1話 ああ、お金がほしいわ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-evening",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、お金がほしいわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ I want money…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ど、どうしたんですか、いきなり……\nでも、ないですね。いつもお金の話ばかりしてますし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wh‚ what's wrong‚ all of a sudden…\nWell‚ actually not a sudden. You always talk about money.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "失礼ですね、人を金の亡者みたいに\n年末は何かと出費がかさむので、ただの愚痴です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How rude‚ you are treating me like money-mad.\nIt's just a complaint‚ because expenses pile up at the end of the year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.5666669846,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ新曲出ますし、クリスマスにはライブもありますし\n仕事があれば、ギャラも入るからいいんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ we have a new song coming out‚ and a live concert on Christmas.\nIf there's work‚ the pay will come in‚ so it’s fine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.2000003179,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "ただ年末は、テレビの収録スケジュールやら何やら\n前倒しになって、きついったら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But at the end of the year‚ things like TV recording schedules and whatnot\nget moved up‚ so it’s tough.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.83333505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "厳しい日程でお願いしてしまって、すみません……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry for asking you to work on such a tight schedule…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.5000017167,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "まー、kanaは仕事ぎちぎちの中でも\n楽しそうにクリスマス配信の仕込みをしてますし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ even in this hectic‚ kana seems to be enjoying\npreparing for the Christmas live stream.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.03333505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "私も正直、浮かれたカップル眺めてたって\n鬱陶しいだけですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To be honest‚ I just find it annoying\nto look at lovey-dovey couples.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.9666683834,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "mihoだけはこの時期になると\nいつにも増して辛気くさいですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At this time‚ only miho gets\neven more gloomy than usual.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.2666711808,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "でも、忙しいうちが華とはいえ\nちょっとくらい、年末らしいこともしたいですねぇ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However‚ even though it is said that busy times are the best‚\nI’d like to do something to feel the end of the year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.3000040055,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "年末らしいもの……年末……うーん\nああ、年末の宝くじなんてのもありましたっけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Year-end vibes… End of the year… Hmm…\nAh‚ there’s the year-end jumbo lottery.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.7000040055,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "……ああ\n確かに、そんなものもありましたねぇ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah.\nRight‚ there is such a thing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.9333327612,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.3999994279
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.3999994279
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "う～、寒っ\n芸能人って普通、タクシーとか車で移動しますよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ughh‚ it’s cold.\nCelebrities usually travel by taxi or car‚ don’t they?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.2000040055,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.5666706722
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "なんでうちだけ毎度、電車なんですか\nかき入れ時にアイドルが風邪引いたらどうするんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why do we always take the train?\nWhat are you gonna do if an idol catches a cold during the peak season?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.5666706722,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.0666706722
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "け、経費削減にご協力下さい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "P‚ please cooperate in cutting expenses…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.0666706722,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor012.m4a",
      "text": "三枝さんにちゃんと言っといて下さいよ\n……そういえば、あそこに見える宝くじ売り場",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Make sure you tell Saegusa-san this properly.\n…Come to think of it‚ that lottery booth we see over there.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.1333373388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.3333373388
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor013.m4a",
      "text": "あそこの売り場\n何度も高額当選者が出てるんで、有名らしいですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That booth\nis apparently famous for having many big winners.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.8333373388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor014.m4a",
      "text": "ま、ただの確率の問題だと思いますけどね\n店員が笑顔の売り場で買うと当たるなんて言いますけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I just think it’s a matter of probability.\nPeople say you’ll win if you buy lotteries from booths with smiling clerks‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.5333373388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor015.m4a",
      "text": "結局、愛想がいい所で買う人が多いから\n母数が多い分、当選者数も増えるってだけのことですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but it's just because many people buy lotteries there due to nice clerks.\nAs a result‚ the number of winners simply increases by the larger sample size.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.2333373388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.9333373388
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "へぇ……\nfranさんも、宝くじ買ったりするんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Heh…\nDo you buy lottery tickets too‚ fran-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.3333373388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor016.m4a",
      "text": "あんな運任せのものに手を出したりしませんよ\nどうせ当たる確率なんて、二千万分の一なんですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t dabble in things that rely on luck.\nThe probability of winning is one in twenty million anyway.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.8333373388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.1333373388
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor017.m4a",
      "text": "……日本だと一等前後賞でもせいぜい数億円ですけど\n海外だと六百億が出たこともあるらしいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…In Japan‚ even if you win first place‚ the prize is only a few hundred million yen‚\nbut I heard that there was a six hundred billion yen winner overseas.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.6000040055,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor018.m4a",
      "text": "あ、そういえば、知ってます？\n宝くじって、江戸時代の初期頃からあるらしいですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ by the way‚ do you know this?\nLottery tickets have been around since the early Edo period.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.5000040055,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 158.3333373388
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "さっきから、宝くじの話しかしてませんけど……\nつまり、気になってるんですね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You've been talking about nothing but lottery tickets…\nIn other words‚ you’re curious about it‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.8333373388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "いつも株やってるじゃないですか\nその延長線上と思えば、別に買ってもいいのでは？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You always do stocks.\nIf you think of it as an extension of that‚ isn’t it fine to buy some?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.8333403906,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 170.8333403906
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_05_01-kor019.m4a",
      "text": "株をギャンブルみたいに言わないで下さい\nあれはれっきとした経済学です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't treat stocks like gambling.\nThat’s a proper economics.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.0333403906,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 176.6333403906
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
